{"tid":2254091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"徐睿知好有料「雙球快掉出」！　胸前挖超深踏上釜日電影節紅毯","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T08:47:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"527c62a6274244950b88f0f1a958e598000d7db5","tid":2254091,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"南韓釜山電影節因疫情延後舉辦，今（22日）晚間延期的「釜日電影節」頒獎典禮正式登場！因韓劇《雖然是精神病但沒關係》火紅的女主角徐睿知，身穿超低胸黑色晚禮服走上紅毯，但挖超低的設計，雙峰隨走動都快要呼之欲出，令人為她捏把冷汗！<br />\n<br />\n徐睿知以黑色長禮服走上釜日電影節紅毯，她纖瘦的身材原來超有料，這次胸前挖空的馬甲設計，讓她雙峰大半部都在外頭「透氣」，低胸的開岔也看起來幾乎要露點，令人看了為她捏把冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n稍早徐睿知以電影《量子物理學（양자물리학）》獲得2020釜日電影節女子人氣明星賞，男子人氣明星賞則由《屍速列車：感染半島》的姜棟元獲得，但他不克出席，以視訊影像代替領獎。<br />\n<br />\n2020釜日電影節本來預計於10月8日，但因疫情關係延後至22日，並以無觀眾方式進行。"},{"pid":"b31626602754ae3ccd7a73207ee428a119a8b85d","tid":2254091,"uid":16659,"like":65,"dislike":41,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5221/e5221631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5221%2Fe5221631.jpg&h=0d84f1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5221/e5221632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5221%2Fe5221632.jpg&h=830bf654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5221/e5221638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5221%2Fe5221638.jpg&h=12cbea9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5221/e5221633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5221%2Fe5221633.jpg&h=4fa1f6ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62238b4f5a9698d6c425aec3cd93980314d47639","tid":2254091,"uid":256952,"like":15,"dislike":23,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"靚到......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/